<item>
            <title>[LU-6025] lctl nodemap commands stop working in interactive mode</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6025</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The nodemap commands that use --long options stop working in interactive mode because optind is not being reset between calls to getopt_long(). I&apos;m uploading a patch that correctly resets optind. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
